OL,3,CCharlotte's Law legislation to be
OL,4,Cbrought forward by Justice Minister
OL,5,CNaomi Long
OL,7,FThe Justice Minister has confirmed
OL,8,Fthat she intends to bring forward
OL,9,Flegislation in support of Charlotte's
OL,10,FLaw.
OL,12,FUnder this legislation, murderers
OL,13,Fwould face tougher sentences if they
OL,14,Fdid not disclose the location of a
OL,15,Fvictim's remains. There would also be
OL,16,Fincentives for co-operation.
OL,18,FThe Law is named after Charlotte
OL,19,FMurray, who was murdered and secretly
OL,20,Fburied by her ex-partner.
